	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=/db/item.html?item=14982&mid=103231563345241>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=/db/item.html?item=14982&mid=103231563345241>Everything you wanted to know about Windstones but were afri</a> <a id=fs8 href=/db/item.html?item=14982&mid=103231563345241#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Tue, Sep 17th 10:35 PM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=100518><span id= >Meirril</span></a><br><span id=notbold>205 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.32]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Windstones are used to make powdered windstones. (2 windstones combined in a pestle = 1 powered windstone.) This is used to make Combine Temper (1 powered windstone + 1 essense of wind + 1 vial of clear mana = combine temper). Combine Temper is used to forge Acrylia armors (go to EQTraders.com and look it up yourself.). Acrylia armor is fairly nice stuff, and a good rout to take towards becomming a grandmaster smith. Unfortunatly, two of the ingredients are rare drops (essense of wind and windstone). Truely unfortunate is the fact that you need 2 windstone for every essence. <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;So, where do you get these windstones? My current sources say Craig Li (the blue/air aliens) in Tenebous Mountains, and Grimlings (any) in Tenebous Mountains. So far, it  appears that grimlings in other zones don't drop windstone. Also, if anyone can confirm that twilight elementals drop windstone I'd appreciate it. I've cleared the island 3 times and have not gotten a single one (have gotten all old world drops, plus essence of wind/fire, reserch components, and spiny weapons.)<br>   Currently, you can occasionaly find 1 on a vendor in Katta for about 21pp, or go to the bazaar (in Fennin Ro) and pick one up for around 100pp. I don't expect the price of these to go up any further because the armor only sells for 1.5-2k (depending on the peice. BP goes for around 2k, but not enough for sale to determin a stable price.). <br><br>Meirril, Fennin Ro</p>&nbsp;<br>Meirril, Fennin Ro</td></tr>
